headline: Bloom Releases First-Ever Special Edition Sparkling Energy: Crisp Apple
summary: Bloom Nutrition, one of the fastest-growing wellness brands of the decade, right in time for fall welcomes its first-ever special edition Sparkling Energy flavor: Crisp Apple. Available now exclusively at Target, this delicious sparkling cider-inspired flavor captures the essence of the season and evokes nostalgia, transporting consumers to a fall state of mind.
